### VMJ sidecar endpoint tests for IntelliJ HTTP Client
### 1) Start scheduler service locally (without vmauth/vmagent)
### 2) Generate binary remote-write payload files:
###    python scripts/generate_remote_write_payloads.py
### 3) Run requests below

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/vmj/health

### sidecar write path (expects biz_date label)
POST {{baseUrl}}/vmj/api/v1/write
Content-Type: application/x-protobuf
Content-Encoding: snappy

< ../tmp/biz_date_remote_write.bin
